          }
        },
        "review_y87bEM": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>\"The three perfumes I received are very good. They last a long time and smell as they should. I was only dissatisfied with the time it took to receive them. But honestly, I placed a second order, so just expect a delay. Haha!<br/>\"</p>",
