            "content": "<p>\"After a small delay, I finally received my Magic Perfume perfumes and they are exactly as they should be! I can hardly believe how much they match the originals — for reference, I received \"Ylang Ylang Rose Jasmine\" and \"Aldehydes Rose Sandalwood\", these are really beautiful fragrances.\"</p>",
            "author": "Gabriella K",
            "date": "7 months ago",
            "rating": 5,
            "show_verified_badge": true,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "review_ARjGGY": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>\"Very good brand, I love the packaging and the aroma.\"</p>",
            "author": "Rosa B",
            "date": "7 months ago",
            "rating": 5,
            "show_verified_badge": true,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "review_qqhj9n": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>\"I'm a big fan of cologne, so I'm picky about clones, but Magic Perfume completely convinced me. I ordered the Sauvage clone from the homepage and immediately recognized the scent when spraying it. I now own 4 Magic Perfume perfumes in total and I love them all. I have 3 more on the way thanks to their bundle deals. If you want something that works on a small budget and offers designer performance, I can't recommend them enough.\"</p>",
            "author": "Sean P",
            "date": "4 months ago",
            "rating": 5,
            "show_verified_badge": true,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "review_7wpFpb": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>\"I am very satisfied with the perfume from this brand, they have such a beautiful perfume like the original and cheaper, I will definitely buy again.\"</p>",
            "author": "Angel",
            "date": "8 months ago",
            "rating": 5,
            "show_verified_badge": true,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "review_7Uhn4n": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>\"This summer, I received a sample of Creed Aventus as a gift and really liked it, but I couldn't buy the original, so I looked for dupes. I found Magic Perfume and ordered \"Pineapple Smoke Vanilla\", it arrived in about a week and smells really good, as close to my original sample, very satisfied with the product, especially for the price.\"</p>",
            "author": "Hwan H",
            "date": "8 months ago",
            "rating": 5,
            "show_verified_badge": true,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "review_mUwEE4": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>\"I tried their 7.5 ml samples and to my great surprise, I loved them. I placed a 2nd order, but this time I took the larger bottles. I must say I received my orders on time and they delivered the fragrances I love!\"</p>",
            "author": "Lauri E",
            "date": "8 months ago",
            "rating": 5,
            "show_verified_badge": true,
            "product": ""
          }
        }
